Russia to Avoid Court With Ukraine Over Gas, Interfax Reports

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-09-14T17:35:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/russia-to-avoid-court-with-ukraine-over-gas-interfax-reports.html
Russia will seek to avoid
international court trials with Ukraine over the terms of
natural-gas shipments, Interfax reported, citing an unnamed
official at the Foreign Affairs Ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
